<item>
            <title>[LU-5634] lshowmount returns no clients and exports stats not incrementing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5634</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For one of our filesystems, on both the MDS and OSS machines client export stats stopped updating. I am not sure when it happened.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also see &quot;lshowmount&quot; only detectes the other server exports, not any clients.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Otherwise, things seem to be operating fine. I disconnected and reconnected some clients, that worked fine. All the other non-export stats are incrementing normally. Don&apos;t see anything in the logs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m stumped.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>lustre 2.5.1-2 on servers, clients 2.4.2 and 2.6.0-2 - centos 6</environment>
